{"tid":1952263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個A0毒撚 早幾個月同腦細同事唱k...","createTime":"2020-03-31T13:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T13:29:53.000Z","uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85664682a783b64f651fd9305f15d07417328da1","tid":1952263,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:21:35.000Z","msg":"話說早幾個月 小弟fg無幾耐 搵到份工喺中環寫字樓做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁返咗工無幾耐 有一日啲同事就叫我一齊K buffet 有個mk男同事仲喺啲女同事嘲諷我 &quot;阿輝咁毒 一定好少去唱k啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到k房之後 我揀咗許美靜嘅明知故犯 我唱咗幾句 成班同事都話我好唱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連個腦細都話估我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相反嗰個mk男同事唱櫻花樹下 佢唱得仲衰過比比鳥 破哂音 直頭好似破地獄咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後嗰個mk男同事話去一去廁所 去咗半個鐘都未返嚟 跟住收到佢喺群組嘅whatsapp 佢話有啲唔舒服 所以返一返屋企先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989755d035793bd13b0b607a24737e0379cfc971","tid":1952263,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"有個mk男同事仲喺啲女同事嘲諷我 &quot;阿輝咁毒 一定好少去唱k啦<br />\n<br />\n????"},{"pid":"a9fc848fc30569a7a631fa153a802935cf1324f5","tid":1952263,"uid":164163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989755d035793bd13b0b607a24737e0379cfc971","tid":1952263,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"有個mk男同事仲喺啲女同事嘲諷我 &quot;阿輝咁毒 一定好少去唱k啦<br />\n<br />\n????"},"citedBy":0,"reply